Corbet &amp; Hill (1992), Findley (1972), Flannery (1995a), Helgen (2007a), Hutson, 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF346A8BFB7F9E971ADFB3D5" box="[1155,1247,2254,2279]" country="Jamaica" name="Kingston" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">Kingston</collectingRegion>
&amp; Francis (2008e), Koopman (1994), Meinig (2002, 2013), Simmons (2005), Tate (1941d), Thomas (1910b), Wiantoro (2011).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
